import sys

n, m, r = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
s = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))
b = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))

ans = 0

for i in range(n):
    if r >= s[i]:
        ans += s[i]
        r -= s[i]

for i in range(m):
    if ans >= b[i]:
        ans -= b[i]
        r += b[i]

print(ans)
